    =staves=
(staffs?)

staves are mana reservoirs.
they cannot be recharged.
you can equip one at a time, but carry
 as many as you like (significantly, limited by
 weight -- staves are heavy)

staves have the following attributes:
        - power (SP)
        - damage

    =talismans=
each talisman you _carry_ increases your trap
spotting skill by one. limited by weight only.

talismans of health similarly increase your HP
by one, these are very rare.

    =potions?=
minor consumable healing items for players
who haven't found a healing spell yet.
